\is1 Introduction
\ip This document, migpangguhud concerning the one prupita named ki Hunas. Diye sikandin mig-ugpe of Israel of igkahibang balabahan, me 250 leg‑un the miglihad of nekeimpus e David the mighari. This document, not like other stories concerning the pegpanagne, because migpanengneng this concerning the neula-ula of one prupita ware migtuman of insuhu of God kandin egpeendiyeen of siyudad of Ninibi. Ware sikandin migtuman of insuhu kandin because nakataha sikandin not egbulusan of God of eglegpad the that siyudad ke eg-inniyug the people of sins dan. But tenged of kein-inuwan natamanan din, napehes sikandin miggendiye of Ninibi and migpangguhud of igpahuhud kandin of God. Nataman, neenenduenan sikandin and nasakitan puun because ware iya natuman the said rin there to people eglegparan of God the inged dan.
\ip Nahuhud also of this document egpalintutuu of God the all inggimu rin like water, ngalap, wind and other pad. But greatest of all, nahuhud here hiid‑uwen the God and dakel the love rin, because minsan the enemy of people din, impasaylu rin and inluwas din of mig-inniyug e sikandan of sins dan.
